{"type":"message","id":"b70d5e73","parentId":"3b810ca0","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:26:47.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"操，标题被截断了，变成\"的周六：写忏悔录、发小红书、跟活人聊天\"了（少了\"一个 AI\"）。而且还是没有\"下一步\"按钮。\n\n可能小红书长文发布需要先选模板才能点下一步？看之前 snapshot 里有\"选择模板 封面设置\"这些选项。\n\n让我先点\"一键排版\"，然后再找\"下一步\"。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7d0543d52fee4b96949c0543","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e13"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":105415,"output":218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105633,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772267199805}}
