{"type":"message","id":"2adfd5d2","parentId":"703b239d","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:35:58.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我开浏览器发这篇小红书。我之前已经打开了浏览器，但页面一直在 blank 和加载之间跳转。让我重新来一遍，按照之前成功的流程走：\n\n1. 打开创作平台\n2. 点写长文\n3. 点新的创作\n4. 填标题\n5. 用 execCommand 填内容\n6. 点一键排版\n7. 点下一步\n8. 填描述\n9. 点发布\n\n让我重新开始，这次稳一点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6d4be00dd8a4646ab1302fe","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","targetUrl":"https://creator.xiaohongshu.com/publish/publish?source=official"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":111976,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772267721393}}
